Job Details
Receptionist - A leading electrical Trading firm requires an Female Office Assistant cum Receptionist for their office in Musaffah, Abu Dhabi.
Requirements
Candidates on husband/father's visa preferred. Requirements: Should have excellent communication and interpersonal skills. Computer literacy is a must. Arabic speaking will be an added advantage. Interested candidates may forward their CV to: hr@megapowerllc.com
